title: Salty Customs with 4Eva

embed.description: Welcome to Salty customs with 4Eva in which the FA teamspeak enjoys an even team of 5v5 randomly chosen from members and guests of the Fallen Angelz clan. Will Mr4Eva prove himself competent at Lee sin? Or Will he feed uncontrollably creating huge salt within the FA Teamspeak.
